Name: Average duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' before transitioning to 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Total duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' across all cases
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - Implementation and the end of the case

Name: Minimum duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' before any subsequent activity
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - Implementation and the end of the case

Name: Maximum duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' before transitioning to 'Accepted + In Progress'
Metric: The maximum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Average duration difference between 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' and 'Accepted + Wait - User'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - User'

Name: Total duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' in cases leading to 'Completed + Closed' without 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Average duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' in cases with 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' preceding it
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' and the end of case where activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment occurs

Name: Maximum duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' across cases with 'High' impact
Metric: the maximum of the duration between the first time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' and the last time instant when <ppinot4py.model.states.RuntimeState object at 0x000001E8EF99C100> - AppliesTo.PROCESS filtered by the function ma == 'High' where ma is the last value of impact

Name: Duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' in the shortest path to case closure
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - Implementation and the end of the case

Name: Duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' in the longest path to case resolution
Metric: the maximum of the duration between the first time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' and the last time instant when <ppinot4py.model.states.RuntimeState object at 0x000001E8EF99C100> - AppliesTo.PROCESS

Name: Average duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' in cases that involve 'Accepted + Assigned' before it
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' and the end of case where activity 'Accepted + Assigned occurs

Name: Minimum duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' in cases ending with 'Completed + Cancelled'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Average duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' in cases with more than 5 activities before it
Duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' in cases with 'Medium' impact compared to 'Low' impact
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' and the end of case grouped by the last value of impact filtered by the function ma == 'Medium' where ma is the last value of impact
